{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Nahtans gahje fawa Namimâ. Un tas KUNGA fit-te to Behrnu/ ko Urijafa Seewa Dahwidam bij dsemdejſi/ ka tas fohti neweffels tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids mekleja Deewu par to Puifenü/ un Dah-wids gaweja/ un eegabje/ un gul-leja pahr Nakti pee Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs wiſſi Wez-zajee winna Namma pee winna/ un gribbeja wiſſu no Semmes uſzelt / bet wiſſch ne gribbeja/ un ne ehde ar teem Maifti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un feptitâ Deena nomir-re tas Behrns. Un Dahwida Kalpi bihjajabs winnam paſaz-ziht/ ka tas Behrns bija nomir-ris. Jo tee fazzija: Raugi / ka-mehr tas Behrns wehl dſihwoja/ tad runnajam mehs ar to / un wiſſch ne gribbeja muhsu Balks-nei klausibt / ka warreſim mehs tad us winnu fazzijt : Tas Behrns irr nomirris / jo wiſſch wehl flimmaki turrefees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Dahwids redſeja/ ka winna Kalpi fluſſinam fawa Starpâ runnaja/ tad famannija Dahwids to Behrnu effam no-mirriſchu/ un Dahwids fazzija us fatweem Kalpeim : Woj tas Behrns nomirre? un tee fazzija: nomirre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Dahwids no Semmes / un maſgajahs/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fwaizija few/ un pahtnihja ta-was Drehbes/ un nahze ta KUN-GA Namimâ / un peeluhdſe. Pebz nahze wiſſch fawa Nam-mâ/ un pawehleja ka few bij Mai-fti preekſcha zelt/ un wiſſch ehde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija winna Kalpi us winnu : Kaſ ta par Leeta/ ko tu darri? Eekams tas Behrns dſihwoja/ tad tu gaweji un rau-daji/ un ka nu tas Behrns no-mirris/ tad effi tu zehlees / un Maifti ehdis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch fazzija: Kad tas Behrns wehl dſihwoja/ tad es gaweju un randaju/ jo esdoh-maju/ ko finn/ ja tas KUNGA pahr mann apſchehlofees/ ka tas Behrns dſihws paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet nu tas nomirris irr/ kapehz bij man gaweht / woj es to warrefchu atkaſ atwest / gann es pee winna eefchu / bet wiſſch pee manis atpakat ne greesifees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to eepreezinaja Dah-wids Batsebu fawn Seewu/ un eegahje pee tahs/ un gulieja pee tahs. Un ta dsemdeja weenâ Dehlu/ un noſauze winna Wahrdü Salamans/ un tas KUNGA mihtleja to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch eedewe to tam Praueetam Nahtanam Rohkâ/ tas noſauze winna Wahrdü Je-didja/ ta KUNGA deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Joabs tad karroja prett Rabbu to Ammona Behrnu / un usnehme to kehnisku Pils-fahtu.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
